Name: allowusermoves
Type: SWITCH
Default-Value: 0
Last-Modified: 2.3.17

Allow moving user accounts (with associated meta-data) via RENAME or XFER.

Note that measures should be taken to make sure that the user being moved
is not logged in, and cannot login during the move.  Failure to do so may
result in the user's meta-data (seen state, subscriptions, etc) being
corrupted or out of date.
